SIMPLE: wherefore
RECORDS: 2

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Wherefore
<hw>Where"fore</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv. & conj.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Where</ets> + <ets>for</ets>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>For which reason; so; -- used relatively.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Wherefore</qex> by their fruits ye shall know them.</q>
<rj><qau>Matt. vii. 20.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>For what reason; why; -- used
interrogatively.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>But <qex>wherefore</qex> that I tell my tale.</q>
<rj><qau>Chaucer.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Wherefore</qex> didst thou doubt?</q> <rj><qau>Matt. xiv.
31.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Wherefore</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Wherefore
<hw>Where"fore</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>the reason why.</def>
<mark>[Colloq.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Wherefrom</ent>⟦br⟧
